::Switchblade::
He forces himself to turn away from the interesting stuff happening 
in front of him. "Oh, hey Decapitron, as far as I know, one of the 
prisoners his here, with me, Megs, Beastbox, and Fireblade. The 
other prisoner should still be outside, unless someone moved 
him... and make SURE the Terrorcons dont get a hold of any 
prisoners." He shudders, and turns back to the action.

On 25 Mar 2001, at 15:45, dcoburn wrote:

> ::Decapitron::
> 
>      Decapitron wasn't sure.
> 
>     "I'm not sure when, I better contact Switchblade, he seems to be dealing with the prisoners," Decapitron answered.
> 
>     Decapitron opened his comm-link to Switchblade.
> 
>     "Switchblade, are the prisoners in their cells where they belong?  If not, get them there, me and Scourge have gotten orders from Megatron to guard them," Decapitron said.
>
